WEBVTT

00:03:56.678 --> 00:04:00.030
from the media and popular
culture at every turn.

00:04:00.054 --> 00:04:01.627
Right? Wrinkles are ugly.

00:04:01.651 --> 00:04:03.168
Old people are pathetic.

00:04:03.192 --> 00:04:05.019
It's sad to be old.

00:04:05.043 --> 00:04:06.434
Look at Hollywood.

00:04:06.458 --> 00:04:08.562
A survey of recent
Best Picture nominations

00:04:08.586 --> 00:04:12.359
found that only 12 percent
of speaking or named characters

00:04:12.383 --> 00:04:13.889
were age 60 and up,

00:04:13.913 --> 00:04:16.534
and many of them
were portrayed as impaired.

00:04:17.025 --> 00:04:19.067
Older people can be
the most ageist of all,

00:04:19.091 --> 00:04:22.335
because we've had a lifetime
to internalize these messages

00:04:22.359 --> 00:04:24.839
and we've never thought to challenge them.

00:04:24.863 --> 00:04:26.349
I had to acknowledge it

00:04:26.373 --> 00:04:27.697
and stop colluding.

